Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.86,0:23:19.15,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Watashi ga watashi no koto wo aishite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.15,0:23:22.18,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Nani ga warui no? shitto deshou ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:24.97,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Itai da to ka kawatteru to ka
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:27.97,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Todokimasen ne, sono ripurai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:30.26,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Daisuki na oyoufuku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:33.39,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Daisuki na okeshou de
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:38.04,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Okimari no haafu tsuin maite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.04,0:23:39.56,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Odekake shiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:42.56,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,HIgasa motte bocchi datte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:45.58,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Shiawase da mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.94,0:23:48.58,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Chu! kawaikute gomen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.58,0:23:51.60,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Umarete kichatte gomen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:54.60,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Chu! Azatokute gomen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:57.42,Roshidere Karaoke,,0,0,0,,Kini nacchau yo ne? Gomen
